snippet: National Football League Commissioner Roger Goodell said on Wednesday that China is too big a market to ignore and the league is working on holding a regular season game there within the next couple of years....
lead_paragraph: National Football League Commissioner Roger Goodell said on Wednesday that China is too big a market to ignore and the league is working on holding a regular season game there within the next couple of years.

headline.main: NFL Looking at Playing Regular Season Game in China
headline.print_headline: NFL Looking at Playing Regular Season Game in China
